# --- Copyrighted ROM data — NEVER commit. Supply your own via `make rom`. ---
games/*/rom/*.bin
games/*/rom/*.zip

# --- Copyrighted AUDIO — NEVER commit. Recorded from YOUR ROM on YOUR machine
#     by games/<game>/tools/record_samples.py (see that dir's README-samples.md).
#     Same posture as the ROM data above: the repo ships the tool, not the sound.
games/*/audio/samples/

